title: YNot Italian
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An Italian restaurant that can cater to vegans. Has Daiya cheese for menu items like the pizza, calzone, and as topping for pasta. There is a separate create-your-own salad bar with an array of vegetable toppings. Staff is accommodating when you let them know if you are vegan.
